Starring : Dermot Mulroney, Augustus Prew, Odette Annable, Reshma ShettyGenre: Medical dramaSeasons: 1 James Bell, a technology revolutionist, built a hospital that uses only the most advanced technology in its treatment processes. Since he is a technology genius James seeks the help of Dr. Wallace to run the medicine side of the hospital. Wallace soon finds out that James has a rare and incurable disease. Did James really build the hospital to save the people or is it about saving himself after all? Set in a technology utopia, Pure Genius is provides more excitement for the technological potential than the actual medical drama.